{"tid":1931112,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"25 歲手足感染武肺","createTime":"2020-03-18T03:56:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T07:17:37.000Z","uid":222614,"like":21,"dislike":97,"uniUserReply":102,"replies":[{"pid":"3638ff9d2a1c92d7a307fa8560d17ff193a06b8e","tid":1931112,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T03:56:17.000Z","msg":"第167號個案：25歲男子，為空中服務員，過往健康良好，居於牛池灣街彩輝邨彩華樓。病人沒有出現病徵，由於國泰航空通知他曾當值的航班有確診病人，病人於3月16日往東九龍普通科門診診所求診，其深喉唾液樣本周二證實呈陽性反應，將會安排入住聯合醫院接受治療，情況穩定。男子3月5日在香港往波士頓的國泰航空CX812商務艙執勤，逗留波士頓數天。其後於從波士頓往香港的國泰航空CX811商務艙再執勤及在3月10日抵港，在機上曾服務第147及148號個案，居於山頂的夫婦。患者同住的父母沒有出現病徵，將被安排接受檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200318/WP3NA5IFOKKNMBPNMX73CQNFFM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200318%2FWP3NA5IFOKKNMBPNMX73CQNFFM%2F&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqFxTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=15a62d86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200318%2FWP3NA5IFOKKNMBPNMX73CQNFFM%2F&h=de087c64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200318/WP3NA5IFOKKNMBPNMX73CQNFFM/</a>"},{"pid":"3815b5d547e575a33311804a38ffab25952bfb14","tid":1931112,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":21,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T03:56:32.000Z","msg":"手足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f492da400886de9b277b73bad6e93068a7301cc","tid":1931112,"uid":201374,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T03:56:39.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2849a773e28c794de150ef80ab0e3ab2008e9374","tid":1931112,"uid":56305,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T03:57:12.000Z","msg":"行動post<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D2n66ak.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD2n66ak.jpg&h=c846716a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XtdqCg1.jpg\" 